data.eml:eml: A new Candonopsini (Ostracoda) genus from subterranean waters of New South Wales (Australia)

This dataset contains the digitized treatments in Plazi based on the original journal article Karanovic, Ivana (2018): A new Candonopsini (Ostracoda) genus from subterranean waters of New South Wales (Australia). Zootaxa 4379 (2): 247-267, DOI: https://doi.org/10.11646/zootaxa.4379.2.6
